FROM maven:3.9-eclipse-temurin-21 AS builder
WORKDIR /build
COPY pom.xml .
RUN mvn dependency:go-offline
COPY src ./src
RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests

FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine
RUN apk add --no-cache fontconfig ttf-dejavu curl

WORKDIR /app

RUN addgroup -g 1001 app && adduser -D -u 1001 -G app app

RUN mkdir -p /tmp/certs && \
    cd /tmp/certs && \
    curl -s https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/global/global-bundle.pem -o aws-rds-ca.pem && \
    curl -s https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt.pem -o azure-digicert-ca.pem && \
    keytool -import -alias aws-rds-ca -file aws-rds-ca.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    keytool -import -alias azure-digicert-ca -file azure-digicert-ca.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm -rf /tmp/certs

COPY --from=builder /build/target/app.jar /app/app.jar
RUN chown -R app:app /app

USER app

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=10s --start-period=40s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

CMD ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
